-- MOVES-RMB Morgan Stanley appoints Matthew Rattray as CEO
-- 
-- Tue Sep 23, 2014 08:34AM EDT
-- None



Sept 23 (Reuters) - RMB Morgan Stanley Ltd, a joint venture between Morgan Stanley International Holdings Inc and RMB Investment & Advisory (Pty) Ltd, said it appointed deputy chief executive Matthew Rattray as its CEO, effective October-end.

Rattray will replace Chris Meyer, who is stepping down to join South Africa's Rand Merchant Insurance Holdings Ltd <RMIJ.J>, RMB Morgan Stanley said.